# Document workspace editState (preview vs edit)

## Model

Each opened document tab in **`S_FaOpenedDocuments`** carries **`editState: boolean`** on **`I_faOpenedDocumentTab`** (**`types/I_faOpenedDocumentsDomain.ts`**).

| editState | Mode | UX |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **`false`** (default) | Preview / viewing | Read-only presentation — no editable inputs |
| **`true`** | Edit | Editable controls for document fields |

- New tabs: **`FA_OPENED_DOCUMENT_DEFAULT_EDIT_STATE`** (**`false`**) via **`createFaOpenedDocumentTabFromOpenMeta`**
- Persisted in **`opened_documents.snapshot_json`** (**`editState`** on each tab row; legacy rows default **`false`** on parse)
- Toggle UI / store action to flip **`editState`** — **`ProjectAppControlBar`** strip buttons (**Edit**, **Save**, **Save without exiting edit mode**); store **`enterDocumentEditMode`**, **`saveDocumentDisplayName`**

## Pure helpers (level 1)

**`src/scripts/openedDocuments/functions/openedDocumentEditStateDomain.ts`**

| Export | Role |
| --- | --- |
| **`resolveOpenedDocumentTabIsInPreviewMode`** | **`!editState`** |
| **`resolveOpenedDocumentTabIsInEditMode`** | **`editState`** |
| **`resolveOpenedDocumentDisplayNameFromTab`** | Preview heading / tab label text |
| **`normalizeOpenedDocumentTabEditState`** | Hydration default for legacy tabs |

**`functions/`** modules: **`import type`** from **`app/types/**`** only — inject helpers from **`*_manager.ts`** / store wiring into composable factories.

## DocumentWorkspacePage field pattern

**`DocumentWorkspacePage.vue`** + **`createUseDocumentWorkspacePage`**

For **each** document field (name, template fields, body, …):

1. **Preview branch** — read-only markup (today: **`<h4>`** + **`previewDisplayName`** for document name)
2. **Edit branch** — existing inputs (**`q-input`**, pickers, etc.) gated on **`documentShowsEditFields`**
3. **Never** show editable inputs when **`documentShowsPreview`** unless product explicitly requires inline edit in preview (not default)

**`data-test-locator`**: preview **`documentWorkspacePage-previewTitle`**; edit name **`documentWorkspacePage-nameInput`**.

Composable exposes **`documentShowsPreview`**, **`documentShowsEditFields`**, **`previewDisplayName`** from active tab **`editState`**.

## Adding a new field (checklist)

1. Store draft/saved on tab or load from project IPC — unchanged by editState
2. Preview: static/read-only element with resolved display value
3. Edit: input only inside **`v-if="documentShowsEditFields"`** (or field-specific flag derived from **`editState`**)
4. Vitest: preview hides inputs; edit shows inputs (mock tab **`editState`** true/false)
5. Changelog when user-visible

